{"itemid":1515,"subject":"Windhaven Comes to Comics","event":"Maris of Lesser Amberly, hero of the popular (Hugo-nominated) series of Windhaven novellas that I wrote with my friend Lisa Tuttle back in the late 70s and early 80s, will soon be taking wing again.&nbsp; I am delighted to announce that we&#39;ve closed a deal with Random House to adapt WINDHAVEN as a graphic novel.\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Windhaven\" src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/219600/219600_600.jpg\" title=\"Windhaven\" /><img alt=\"wh003\" src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/219798/219798_600.jpg\" title=\"wh003\" />\r\n\r\nLisa Tuttle herself will be scripting the book, based on our original stories.\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"gm-tuttle\" src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/220243/220243_600.jpg\" title=\"gm-tuttle\" /><img alt=\"images\" src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/220496/220496_600.jpg\" title=\"images\" />\r\n\r\nLisa has already delivered the script... and we&#39;re excited to reveal that we&#39;ve just signed the amazing French artist ELSA CHARRETIER to illustrate the graphic novel.&nbsp; Check out her website at http://elsacharretier.blogspot.com/&nbsp; for links to her work.&nbsp; She&#39;s fantastic, and we cannot wait to see how she brings the world of Windhaven and its fliers to life.","ditemid":387855,"eventtime":"2014-11-04 09:14:00","props":{"current_mood":"pleased","current_location":"Santa Fe","taglist":"graphic novels, random house, windhaven, comic books","current_moodid":109,"commentalter":1415768486,"crosspost_tw":"Windhaven Comes to Comics http://j.mp/1rZ2OYP","opt_lockcomments":1,"picture_keyword":"torcon","opt_screening":"F","personifi_tags":"nterms:yes","revnum":1,"interface":"web","revtime":1415856646},"can_comment":0,"logtime":"2014-11-04 16:13:26","anum":15,"url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/387855.html","event_timestamp":1415092440,"reply_count":24,"comments":[{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejo